{"word":"παιδίον","slug":"παιδίον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>παιδίον, ου, τό</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ dim.\">dim.</a> of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:παῖς\">παῖς</a></el>; age range from a newborn to time of youth] <b>child<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> within a broad range of age, but normally pre-puberty <b><a href='B:480 5:39-41'>Mk 5:39-41</a></b> (a girl of 12 years); <b><a href='B:480 9:24'>9:24</a>, <a href='B:480 9:36'>36f</a>; <a href='B:480 10:15'>10:15</a>; <a href='B:490 11:7'>Lk 11:7</a>; <a href='B:500 4:49'>J 4:49</a>; <a href='B:690 2:14'>1 J 2:14</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on maturation <b><a href='B:490 2:40'>Lk 2:40</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pl.\">pl.</a> <b><a href='B:470 11:16'>Mt 11:16</a>; <a href='B:470 14:21'>14:21</a>; <a href='B:470 18:2'>18:2</a>, <a href='B:470 18:4'>4f</a>; <a href='B:470 19:14'>19:14</a>; <a href='B:480 10:13'>Mk 10:13f</a>.</b> In imagery <b><a href='B:470 18:3'>Mt 18:3</a>; <a href='B:530 14:20'>1 Cor 14:20</a>; <a href='B:650 2:13'>Hb 2:13f</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> specifically of a baby <b><a href='B:470 2:8'>Mt 2:8</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ch.\">ch.</a>; <b><a href='B:490 1:59'>Lk 1:59</a>, <a href='B:490 1:66'>66</a>; <a href='B:490 2:17'>2:17</a>, <a href='B:490 2:27'>27</a>; <a href='B:500 16:21'>J 16:21</a>; <a href='B:650 11:23'>Hb 11:23</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> of adults in endearing address <b><a href='B:500 21:5'>J 21:5</a>; <a href='B:690 2:18'>1 J 2:18</a>; <a href='B:690 3:7'>3:7</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:παιδιόθεν\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:παιδίσκη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}